status-quo.name: Status Quo - Continue Current Vendor Mix
status-quo.description: Continue with current 4-vendor distribution (Stryker, Zimmer, Arthrex, Other). No consolidation, no cost savings.

tri-vendor-premium.name: Tri-Vendor Strategy - Premium Focus
tri-vendor-premium.description: Consolidate to top 3 vendors by volume (Stryker, Zimmer, Arthrex). Negotiate volume-based pricing. Eliminate 'Other' category.

dual-premium.name: Dual-Vendor Premium Strategy
dual-premium.description: Focus on Stryker + Zimmer Biomet as primary vendors. Strong negotiating leverage with 70% volume concentration. Transition Arthrex users.

dual-value.name: Dual-Vendor Balanced Strategy
dual-value.description: Stryker (premium) + Arthrex (value innovation). Clinical excellence with cost optimization. Target reverse shoulder growth.

single-vendor-stryker.name: Single-Vendor Strategy - Stryker
single-vendor-stryker.description: Full consolidation to Stryker as sole shoulder vendor. Maximum negotiating leverage and GPO alignment, but highest surgeon disruption.
